Cell["\<\
This is an exact finite-dimensional contract decision, not yet the full \
microscopic SK completion theorem. It should be read together with the \
exploratory completion notebook: the old appended-block lift remains a \
negative probe, while this notebook records what survives after enforcing the \
split-faithful contract dependencies.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"87ed4804-e5e4-4cb4-9876-15f98c36da19"]
